ng native flowers can significantly aid their survival and welfare.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/world-bee-day-campaign-encourages-public-to-protect-declining-uk-pollinators/articleshow/131230508.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/world-bee-day-campaign-encourages-public-to-protect-declining-uk-pollinators/articleshow/131230508.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-20T21:20:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131230520,imgsize-37528.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scotland: Jenny Gilruth expected to become Deputy First Minister in new SNP team]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131230293.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Scotland's First Minister John Swinney is set to announce his new cabinet. Jenny Gilruth is tipped to become Deputy First Minister. Swinney was sworn in for his second term. His government will focus on the cost-of-living crisis and NHS reforms. The SNP won 58 seats in the recent election. New appointments are expected soon.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/scotland-jenny-gilruth-expected-to-become-deputy-first-minister-in-new-snp-team/articleshow/131230293.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/scotland-jenny-gilruth-expected-to-become-deputy-first-minister-in-new-snp-team/articleshow/131230293.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-20T21:06:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131230298,imgsize-19122.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[78-year-old UK great-grandmother left shaken after utility firm mistakenly declares her dead over £6